title: Airbnb Discover Web App
description: A full-stack application that utilizes Airbnb listings and Yelp business data, as well as Yelp APIs for real-time data integration.

title: Cardiovascular Disease Prediction
description: Performed exploratory data analysis and hyperparameter tuning for machine learning classifiers for predicting cardiovascular disease. Built an interactive web app utilizing the streamlit library for users to interact with the optimized machine learning classifiers and receive prediction results.

title: Mini Google Search Engine
description: Worked in a team of four to develop a search engine, which consisted of components such as the front end, server, web-crawler, indexer and page rank. Deployed the search engine on AWS EC2 instance.
